<h1>Here is a list of all Musicians and the Instruments they play</h1><hr>

<ul>
<% @musicians.each do |musician| %>
  <% if musician.stage_name %>
      <li><%= link_to musician.stage_name, public_path(musician) %></li><br>
      <% musician.instruments.each do |instrument| %>
    <ul>
      <li><%= instrument.name %></li>
    </ul>
      <% end %>
  <% else %>
      <li><%= musician.user.full_name %></li><br>
    <% musician.instruments.each do |instrument| %>
    <ul>
      <li><%= instrument.name %></li></ul><br>
    <% end %>
  <% end %>
<% end %>
</ul>
<hr><hr>

Now that you've seen all these lovely musos, how about looking at a <%= link_to 'list of all Bands', '/bands' %>? Or if you're feeling brave, you could just <%= link_to "create your own new Band", new_band_path %> - do it, Bandroid believes in you!
